short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension to speed up using Google Sheets!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sheet Pro allows you to boost your productivity in Google Sheets.
You can quickly trace cell precedents at the click of a button, allowing you to navigate back through a formula and trace it backwards.
The extension also allows for users to set their own shortcuts for certain existing Sheets shortcuts. 
Hit CTRL  + SHIFT + [ to start tracing!

Other functionalities:
- shortcuts (beta)
- screenshot current selection
